LOVELY!
What a wonderful setting to enjoy a meal.
The Scene... contemporary... a tad intimate but not romantic... upscale restaurant to enjoy a meal.
It was a bit busy today (Sunday around noon) for brunch/lunch... and Everyone wanted to sit outside... so we opted (since we were hungry) to sit inside.
