Mom had a Mimosa... she said it was ok.
The check for the 3 of us... with our 2 alcoholic beverages and 1 coffee was $92 before tip.... this is a bit pricey... but 1) it's the Four Seasons and 2) it's Vegas.
Note... if you order coffee... it's $5.50... personally I think that's a rip off but what do I know.

